messages.message: Now that I think of it… are you working from `master` or a specific release branch?

Synced with Will, I observed this behavior that nginx returns logs as bytes. Turns out it’s something related to SSL - nginx was trying to send encrypted content to a non-secure endpoint. Problem solved by rebuildling nginx locally in docker, but we still don’t know the exact reason of why this bug shows up as i was pulling our prebuilt images and this was fixed a few weeks ago. I’ll let Will know again if I run into the same problem.

Huge thanks to Will helping me out!
